In the morning I get up make the breakfast for my husband and I. Then I see him of to work. After that I get the children up and make their breakfast. I wash them both and put clean clothes on them. Then they go and play with their friends in the backgarden. After that I work all day in the house. I have my dinner with the children then start work again. When its teatime the children and I have tea. After that I put my children to bed at 2o'clock. I get changed ready for my husband coming in. I get out my knitting and finish it of. Then my husband comes in and has tea and we watch the teliviion till ten o'clock then go to bed. On saturday and and sundays we all go to the beach and have a picnic. We have a very happy life.  Words: 151
